    Class Description
    LazyMigration
    This class provides method for migrating entities lazily/topdown based on datalog rules.
    RuleGoalTree
    This class represents a rule goal tree with a top goal and subgoals/children goals: each top down execution has a rule goal tree as a starting point.
    TopDownExecution
    This class executes datalog rules in a top down approach it is derived of MigrationExecution class
